gular heart rhythm, shortness of breath, or syncope.', 'Metabolism', 'Concomitant use of nilotinib with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors such as itraconazole, ketoconazole, posaconazole, voriconazole, conivaptan, nefazodone, cobicistat, delavirdine, protease inhibitors, and ketolide and certain macrolide antibiotics should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/144327/', '', 'Futibatinib, Tucatinib, Alpelisib, Lenvatinib, Trametinib, Nintedanib, Vandetanib, Afatinib, Alectinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Sorafenib', 'Dirithromycin, Lincomycin, Clindamycin', 1767369485);
